102061.「ただいまより 第３回\n アストルティア・クイーン コンテストに\n 参加する:
We are pleased to introduce you to the
beautiful women who will be participating in
the 3rd Annual Astoltia Queen Contest!

102062.「まずは 前回 壮絶な接戦を征し\n 見事 クイーンの座を 勝ち取った\n この:
First, let's start with the last contestant,
who won the title of queen in an epic battle
of wits!

102063.「第２回 アストルティア・クイーン！\n 農村発ニューヒロイン ミシュア！\n:
The 2nd Astoltia Queen! New Heroine from Rural
Mishua, Mishua!

102065.「おどろかせてしまって ごめんなさい。\n 今回は 私の真なる姿……グランゼドー:
I am sorry to have frightened you. This time,
I will be participating as the hero princess
of Gran Zedora, my true self.

102066.「前回 ご投票くださった方も そうでない方も\n 伝説の勇者の 名に恥じぬよう:
Whether you voted for me last time or not, I will fight fair and square to live up to my name as the legendary Hero, so please support
me.

102067.「魔物想いの 優しい心と 大胆な行動力！\n その スーパーハイブリッドなセンス:
He has a kind heart for Monster and a daring
spirit! With his super hybrid sense, he has
recently emerged as a leader!

102068.「第２回 クイーン・コンテスト 第２位！\n アラハギーロの青き導き手 セラフィ:
2nd Queen Contest 2nd Place! Seraphi, the blue
guide of Al-Ahagiro!

102069.「えへへ。前回は 惜しかったよね。\n でも たくさんの人たちが 応援してくれて:
Heh heh. It was so close last time, wasn't it? But I was so happy that so many people cheered for me. I'm looking forward to seeing you
again.

102070.「オーグリード大陸に咲く 一輪の赤いバラ！\n 新世代のライバル達が 台頭する中:
A single red rose blooming in Ogreed Continent! With a new generation of rivals rising to the top, will the first queen show
her determination and regain her throne?

102071.「第２回 クイーン・コンテスト 第３位！\n オーガニック ビューティー マイユ:
2nd Queen Contest 3rd Place! Ogre Nick Beauty
Maille!

102072.「強敵は 増える一方だけど やることは同じよ。\n 己のチカラを信じ 全身全霊で:
The number of strong opponents will only increase, but we have to do the same thing. We just have to believe in our own strength and
challenge them with all our might. I'm sure we will take back the queen's title!

102073.「さて 当初の予定では ここで 前回４位の\n クラハさんを紹介するはずでしたが:
Well, our original plan was to introduce here Klaha, who placed 4th last time, but unfortunately, he is absent due to nursing his
son who caught a cold.

102074.「しかぁし！ 全世界の ママさんファンの皆様！\n ご安心ください。ママといえば:
However! To all the mama-fans in the world!
Don't worry. Speaking of moms, here she is!
She's rushed in from heaven again!

102075.「天然☆予知っ娘ママ アルウェ王妃ちゃん様！: Dear natural and predictable mama Queen Alwe!

102076.「は～い。ミローレさん じょうずじょうずー。\n よばれて とびでた アルウェで:
Yes, Milore-san is very skillful. I'm Alwe, a
freshman. I'm so glad you called me again.

102077.「やっぱし 予知っ娘パワーで\n 結果は 見えてるんだけどぉー う～んとね。\n:
I knew I could see the outcome with the power
of the prediction girl, but... well, you know.
I'm sure it won't happen this time either!

102078.「セレドの町に君臨する 絶対的女王様が\n 絶対的反抗期を終え 改心の一撃！\n:
The absolute queen of the Town of Celed has ended her period of absolute rebellion with a coup de grace! She has transformed into a
lovely maiden!

102080.「可憐な乙女……ですって！？ ほ…ほめても\n 何も出ないわよ。お気に入りの リ:
A dainty maiden, you say? I'm not going to get any compliments from you. I will give you credit for noticing my favorite ribbon,
though.

102081.「とにかく セレドの みんなのためにも\n 今回は 絶対に負けられないの。だから:
Anyway, for the sake of everyone at Celed, we
can't lose this time. So, you there! Why don't
you do me a favor?

102082.「風の町アズランに ひっそりと咲く 月見草！\n 第１回 コンテスト ２位に輝い:
Evening primrose blooms quietly in Wind Town Azlan! Can you ride the whirlwind of generational change with your ability that won
the 2nd place in the 1st contest?

102083.「夢見る風乗り少女 フウラ！: Fuura is a dreamy wind-riding girl!

102084.「も…もうっ。少女じゃないもん。大人だよっ。\n 風乗りのつとめも ちゃんと果た:
Mooooo. I'm not a girl. I'm an adult. I've
done my duty as a wind rider, and with my
adult charm, I'm going to win this time!

102085.「さて ここまでが 前大会までの出場者……。\n ここからは ニューフェイスの登:
Now, here are the contestants up to the
previous rounds. From here on, new faces will
make their appearance.

102086.「グランゼドーラ七不思議の ひとつともされる\n 年齢不詳の 謎多き 美魔女……:
The enigmatic beauty of unknown age is considered one of the Seven Wonders of Gran Zedora! Does the goddess of knowledge conquer
the beauty pageant?

102088.「ふっ。かような催しに 招かれるとは\n 私も まだまだ 捨てたものではないな。:
Phew. To be invited to such an event, I'm
still not so bad after all. Very well. I will
teach you what you want.

102090.「紅玉館の スリーピングビューティー！\n その はかない美しさに 紅丸急上昇中:
Ruby Mansion's Sleeping Beauty! Her beauty is so fragile that her red circle is rapidly growing! With her doctor's permission, she's
making her long-awaited entry!

102091.「箱入りリンゴ娘 レイ・マクフォール！: Apple girl in a box Ray McFaul!

102092.「ビューティーなんて……ゴホッ ゴホッ。\n でも 優勝できたら とても うれし:
Beauty is a big deal. But I would be very
happy if I could win. I am like this, but
please support me.

102093.「アストルティア商業組合の リーサルウェポン！\n 無敵の アクセサリービジネス:
The Lethal Weapon of the Astoltia Commercial Association! Celebrities of the synthetic world awakened by the unbeatable Accessory
business!

102094.「ヴェリナードに住む \n ラスボスと呼ばれた女 合成屋リーネ！:
Synthesizer Renee, a woman called the "Rasbos"
who lives in Verinard!

102095.「ヤッホー。リーネさんだよー！ みんなの熱ーい\n ご要望に おこたえして 出場:
Hey there, it's Renee! In response to everyone's enthusiastic requests, I'm going to participate. I'm going to compete, so I'm
going to win for sure! Okay?

102096.「みんな 私を気に入ってくれるといいな。\n まあ いざとなったら ゴールドパワ:
Hope you guys like me. Well, when push comes
to shove, gold power, anyway! You better pray
it all works out!

102097.「かりそめの玉座で 運命に抗う黒蝶！\n 勇者姫との 因縁の対決に 決着をつける:
The Black Butterfly, defying fate in a throne of transgression! In order to settle the fateful confrontation with the hero princess,
this person has made an emergency entry!

102098.「紫電なる復讐者 魔勇者アンルシア！: Shiden naru avenger Evil Hero Anlucia!

102099.「ミローレとやら……上出来だ。舞台は整ったな。\n これで 存分に知らしめること:
Milore and you've done well. The stage is set. Now we can show her to the fullest. This magical beauty that hero princesses don't
have!

102100.「そして アイツに打ち勝ち 私こそが\n 真の勇者と呼ばれるに ふさわしい存在だ:
And I will defeat him and prove that I am the
one who deserves to be called the true Hero!
All of you, lend me your strength!

102101.「以上 １０名の美女たちが\n クイーンの座をかけて コンテストを争います。:
These 10 beauties will compete for the title
of queen.

102102.「果たして 栄光の座に かがやくのは\n 誰なのか！？\n それを決めるのは あ:
Who will be crowned with glory? It is you who
will decide!

102103.「どうですか <pc>さん。\n 今回も選りすぐりの美女が そろいました。\n:
What do you think ? We have a great selection of beauties for you to choose from this time. Did you find your favorite
one?

102104.「クイーンにふさわしいと思う 美女が決まったら\n その方のチョコ作りを 手伝っ:
If you decide on a beautiful woman who you
think is worthy of being queen, please help
her make the chocolates.

102105.「あなたが チョコ作りを手伝った相手に\n あなたの１票が 投じられるのです。\:
Your vote will go to the person you helped
make the chocolates. Please think carefully
before you make your choice.

102106.「選び終わりましたら お話がありますので\n 私の所に お立ち寄りください。\n:
When you have finished your selection, please
stop by my place for a chat. I'll be outside.

102107.「ただいまより 第３回\n アストルティア・クイーン コンテストの\n 結果発表:
We will now announce the results of the 3rd
Astoltia Queen Contest!

102108.「この ショコラフォンテヌ城の\n クイーンの座は いったい 誰の手に！？\n:
Who will be the queen of the Chocolat Fontenay
Castle? The result will finally be revealed!

102109.「皆さま！ ステージに ご注目ください！:
Ladies and gentlemen! Please pay attention to
the stage!
